rse Drug React Toxicol Rev 14 (1995): 233-54[3] Becquemont L, Verstuyft C, Kerb R, et al. "Effect of grapefruit juice on digoxin pharmacokinetics in humans." Clin Pharmacol Ther 70 (2001): 311-6', 1767369485);
