eng L, Gunderson S, Balzar SA, Johnson BD, Fish JT "Recommendations for the use of medications with continuous enteral nutrition." Am J Health Syst Pharm 66 (2009): 1438-67[4] "Product Information. VFEND (voriconazole)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.[5] "Product Information. Esbriet (pirfenidone)." Intermune Inc, Brisbane, CA.[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0', 1767369485);
